<section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-container">
    <aside class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="avatar-frame">
        <img src="/profile.jpg" alt="Guru" class="profile-avatar" />
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
      <div class="location-info">
        <svg class="location-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9C5 14.25 12 22 12 22C12 22 19 14.25 19 9C19 5.13 15.87 2 12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        </svg>
        <span class="location-text">Washington D.C</span>
      </div>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ilangurudev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="instagram-link" aria-label="Follow on Instagram">
        <svg class="instagram-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
        </svg>
        <span>ilangurudev</span>
      </a>
    </aside>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="bio-text">
        <p>
          Hi, I'm Guru. I'm a photographer and AI engineer exploring the intersection of technology and art.
        </p>
        <p>
          Photography is my way of slowing down. In a world that moves at the speed of algorithms, 
          I use my camera to pause, observe, and appreciate the raw, unscripted beauty of the world around us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="details-grid">
        <div class="detail-block">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Why I Shoot</h3>
          <p>
            To document the ephemeral. I'm drawn to the quiet moments in busy streets, 
            the play of light on architecture, and the vastness of natural landscapes. 
            Every shutter click is an attempt to preserve a feeling that words often fail to capture.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-block">
          <h3 class="detail-title">Gear</h3>
          <ul class="gear-list">
            <li>Body: Sony A7R V</li>
            <li>Sigma 24-70mm f2.8 Art II</li>
            <li>Sigma Contemporary 35mm f2</li>
            <li>Sony GM 50mm f1.4</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.1);
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-sidebar {
    text-align: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: 2rem;
  }

  .avatar-frame {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    padding: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.1);
    background: #fff;
  }

  .profile-avatar {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .location-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .location-icon {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    stroke: currentColor;
    fill: none;
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .location-text {
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }

  .instagram-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    background: #fff;
  }

  .instagram-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--amber);
    color: var(--amber);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.15);
  }

  .instagram-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    stroke: currentColor;
    fill: none;
  }

  .bio-text {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .bio-text p {
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem; /* Slightly larger for intro */
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .details-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.1);
  }

  .detail-title {
    font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  /* Make the line only appear for aesthetics */
  .detail-title::after {
    content: '';
    height: 1px;
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--amber);
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .detail-block p {
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .gear-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack on single col in this small space */
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .gear-list li {
    font-family: 'Work Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  .gear-list li::before {
    content: 'â€¢';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-sidebar {
      position: static;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .section-title {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .instagram-link {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 200px;
    }

    .bio-text {
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .details-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: left;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
